Package airtrafficcontrol.app.utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AirCorridorInTime
    Class whose instances represent an air corridor where it is expected that a certain airship flies during a certain period of time.
    Airliner
    Creates an airliner
    Airship
    Abstract class whose subclasses' instances represent airships.
    Altitude
    This class represents an Altitude value.
    AltitudeComparator
    compares Airships and sorts them out by altitude
    AltitudeCorridor
    Class whose instances represent an altitude air corridor, with a maximum and minimum values of altitude.
    CargoAircraft
    class of civil aircraft used to transport cargo
    CivilAirplane
    super class of all the civilian airplanes
    Database
    Class whose instances are databases of airships.
    FlightPlan
    allows to build the plan of the flight
    GeographicalPosition
    Class whose instances represent geographical positions defined by a value of latitude, a value of longitude and a value of altitude.
    Latitude
    Class whose instances represent a latitude value.
    Longitude
    This class represents a Longitude value.
    MilitaryAirplane
    Abstract class of all the military airplanes
    PrivateJet
    Creates an airliner
    ReadAirplanesCoordinates
    Class that allows a database to update the airplanes' coordinates contained in it using information from a text file.
    ReadListOfFlights
    Class whose instances read a list of flights from a text file and create an instance of Database.
    ReportGenerator
    Allows to emit various types of reports.
    Transport
    Creates a military transport airplane.
